@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Export Document Header Report'
define root view entity ZETR_DDL_I_EXP_HEAD_RPR
  as select from    zetr_t_r101       as Head
    left outer join I_CompanyCode     as company on Head.bukrs = company.CompanyCode

    left outer join I_CountryText     as extco   on  extco.Language = $session.system_language
                                                 and extco.Country  = Head.extco
    left outer join I_CountryText     as desco   on  desco.Language = $session.system_language
                                                 and desco.Country  = Head.desco
    left outer join zetr_t_exp101     as expty   on  expty.langu = $session.system_language
                                                 and expty.expty = Head.expty
    left outer join zetr_t_xexp107    as pymty   on  pymty.spras = $session.system_language
                                                 and pymty.pymty = Head.pymty
    left outer join zetr_t_xexp108    as trnty   on  trnty.spras = $session.system_language
                                                 and trnty.trnty = Head.trnty
    left outer join zetr_t_xexp112    as cuscd   on  cuscd.spras = $session.system_language
                                                 and cuscd.land1 = Head.extco
                                                 and cuscd.cuscd = Head.cuscd
    left outer join I_BusinessPartner as shpfr   on shpfr.BusinessPartner = Head.shpfr
    left outer join I_BusinessPartner as brofr   on brofr.BusinessPartner = Head.brofr
    left outer join I_BusinessPartner as cusof   on cusof.BusinessPartner = Head.cusof
    left outer join I_Customer        as kunrg   on kunrg.Customer = Head.kunrg
    left outer join I_Bank_2          as bnka    on  bnka.BankCountry    = Head.extco
                                                 and bnka.BankInternalID = Head.bankl
{
  key Head.filen,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'expty_txt' ]
      Head.expty,
      expty.descr                                                                                                                                                                        as expty_txt,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'bukrs_txt' ]
      Head.bukrs,
      company.CompanyCodeName                                                                                                                                                            as bukrs_txt,
      Head.descr,
      Head.bldat,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'extco_txt' ]
      Head.extco,
      extco.CountryName                                                                                                                                                                  as extco_txt,
      Head.extrg,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'desco_txt' ]
      Head.desco,
      desco.CountryName                                                                                                                                                                  as desco_txt,
      Head.desrg,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'pymty_txt' ]
      Head.pymty,
      pymty.bezei                                                                                                                                                                        as pymty_txt,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'trnty_txt' ]
      Head.trnty,
      trnty.bezei                                                                                                                                                                        as trnty_txt,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'cuscd_txt' ]
      Head.cuscd,
      cuscd.bezei                                                                                                                                                                        as cuscd_txt,
      Head.cofrp,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'cusof_txt' ]
      Head.cusof,
      cast( case cusof.BusinessPartnerCategory when '1' then concat_with_space(cusof.FirstName, cusof.LastName, 1)
                                               when '2' then concat_with_space(cusof.OrganizationBPName1, cusof.OrganizationBPName2, 1)
                                               when '3' then concat_with_space(cusof.GroupBusinessPartnerName1, cusof.GroupBusinessPartnerName2, 1) else null end as abap.char( 100 ) )  as cusof_txt,
      Head.sfrrp,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'shpfr_txt' ]
      Head.shpfr,
      cast( case shpfr.BusinessPartnerCategory when '1' then concat_with_space(shpfr.FirstName, shpfr.LastName, 1)
                                               when '2' then concat_with_space(shpfr.OrganizationBPName1, shpfr.OrganizationBPName2, 1)
                                               when '3' then concat_with_space(shpfr.GroupBusinessPartnerName1, shpfr.GroupBusinessPartnerName2, 1) else null end as abap.char( 100 ) )  as shpfr_txt,
      Head.bfrrp,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'brofr_txt' ]
      Head.brofr,
      cast( case brofr.BusinessPartnerCategory when '1' then concat_with_space(brofr.FirstName, brofr.LastName, 1)
                                               when '2' then concat_with_space(brofr.OrganizationBPName1, brofr.OrganizationBPName2, 1)
                                               when '3' then concat_with_space(brofr.GroupBusinessPartnerName1, brofr.GroupBusinessPartnerName2, 1 ) else null end as abap.char( 100 ) ) as brofr_txt,
      Head.extfn,
      Head.rexdt,
      Head.cedno,
      Head.ceddt,
      Head.shpdt,
      Head.shpno,
      Head.extdt,
      Head.desdt,
      Head.nopck,
      Head.clsed,
      Head.fldel,
      Head.chind,
      Head.bankl,
      Head.iban,
      bnka.BankName,
      bnka.BankBranch,
      @ObjectModel.text.element: [ 'kunrg_txt' ]
      Head.kunrg,
      cast(concat_with_space(kunrg.OrganizationBPName1, kunrg.OrganizationBPName2, 1) as abap.char( 80 ) )                                                                               as kunrg_txt,
      Head.inc01,
      Head.inc02,
      Head.lcnum,
      Head.plaka,
      Head.snrkp,
      Head.ucsno,
      Head.ucstr,
      Head.hzrtr,
      Head.beyts,
      Head.beysa,
      Head.beyty,
      Head.hatbl,
      Head.gemia,
      Head.sefno,
      Head.sbeyt,
      Head.bolnumber,
      Head.brgew,
      Head.ntgew,
      Head.gewei,
      @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure : 'gewei'
      Head.volum,
      Head.voleh,
      Head.erdat,
      Head.ernam,
      Head.erzet,
      Head.aedat,
      Head.aezet,
      Head.aenam,
      Head.reffn,
      Head.incno
}
